Capacity for Development South Sudan (CFD) is an in South Sudan registered international NGO (operation certificate from RRC), providing Capacity Building support services to Ecorys. As Country director I am responsible for:
-	HR and Payroll management of local staff (15);
-	Logistics / fleet management (inc. UN-HAS travel);
-	Financial management of the NGO;
-	Pipeline development and networking with potential experts.
